      "text": "Ta Mihletaja Sittenti irr \npeetizzigi/ bet prett ta Nihdeta-\nja Skubpſtischannahm (Deews) \njapeeluhds."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pee- ehduſi Dwehfele ir \ntihru Meddu min pa Rahjahm/ \nbet weenai iſtalkuschai Dwehfe-\nlei irr wiſs Ruhktums falds."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka weens Putnis/ kas no \nfawas Ligsdas atstahjahs / ta \npatt irr tas Wihrs/ kas fawn \nWeetu pamett."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Etje un Kwehpja-Sahles \neepreezina to Sirđi/ tik mihligs \nirr kurrain taws Drangs tahs \nDwehfeles Vadohma deht."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ne atstahj tawn Drau-\ngu/ nedś tawa Tehwa Draugu/ \nun ne eij tawa Brahta Namina \ntawn Behdu Laikā/ labbaks irr \nweena Raimuſch Tuwuma/ ne-\nta Brahtis Tahtuma."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Effi gudrs mans Dehls/ \ntad preezakees manna Sirđs/ un"
    },
