      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Prahtigs reds papreekſchu \nto Launu/ un apflepjahs/ un te \nNeprahtigee eet zauri/ un toh-\ntohditi."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jem tam fawu Drehibi \nkas Zittu irr Galwā nehmis/ un \nfihle winnu weena Swesch-\ndeht."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas fawu Tuwaku tei \nar augſtu Balsi rihta agri zelda \nmees/ tas tohp winnam ta pat \ntihdsinahts/ itt ka buhtu ta \nlahdejs."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nemittejama Pilſefcha \nna kad Leetus lihst/ un ween \nRehjeja Seewa stahw ween \nLihdsiba."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas winnu flepi/ tas flep \nto Wehin/ un to Smartchu ni \nEtjes fawa labba Rohka/ kas \ntatschu * ta ohsta tohp.\n* Eebr: Wall: faukta, tas irr kannama dar\nrita."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Weena Dſelfe trin to oh \ntrn/ ta patt trin weens Wihr-\nfawu Tuwaku."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas to Wihges- Kohku \npafarga/ tas ehdihś winna Aug-\ntus/ un kas fawu Kungu far-\nga/ tas taps Godā turrehts:"
    },
